how those emotions get
renewed, and how you really

00:29:40.550 --> 00:29:45.570
deliver the message with
such heart every time.

00:29:45.570 --> 00:29:48.210
KINGLSEY LEGGS: I love being in
shows that are really dramatic

00:29:48.210 --> 00:29:50.320
and have this kind of content.

00:29:50.320 --> 00:29:53.400
But I was just talking
with Suzan-Lori earlier,

00:29:53.400 --> 00:29:55.750
before we started this,
that this, I don't know.

00:29:55.750 --> 00:29:58.040
There's just something very
