00:30:41.420 --> 00:30:43.880
You just want to give it truth.

00:30:43.880 --> 00:30:46.920
You want to give it
all that you have.

00:30:46.920 --> 00:30:51.860
And you want it to reach the
person in the top, in the back.

00:30:51.860 --> 00:30:55.460
So it's just wonderful
to play every night.

00:30:55.460 --> 00:30:58.040
NATHANIEL STAMPLEY:
I'll chime in, also.

00:30:58.040 --> 00:31:01.610
With this particular
production, we

00:31:01.610 --> 00:31:05.430
don't have the trappings of
really huge sets and a really

00:31:05.430 --> 00:31:07.710
large cast.

00:31:07.710 --> 00:31:09.990
So the story is
in the forefront.

00:31:09.990 --> 00:31:13.050
And so that demands a
certain level of commitment

00:31:13.050 --> 00:31:15.630
every single second
you're on the stage.

00:31:15.630 --> 00:31:18.770
So there's nowhere to
hide, first of all.

00:31:18.770 --> 00:31:23.030
And secondly, as you
can sort of sense today,

00:31:23.030 --> 00:31:26.940
we are truly a community
