light as I can offstage.

00:31:38.020 --> 00:31:44.350
I like to laugh and smile
and save my voice, as well.

00:31:44.350 --> 00:31:48.960
So that you're not living in
those really dark and heavy

00:31:48.960 --> 00:31:50.910
moments 24/7.

00:31:50.910 --> 00:31:54.404
Because that's tough to carry
around with you all the time.

00:31:54.404 --> 00:31:56.529
SUMAYYA ALI: I totally have
to decompress and watch

00:31:56.529 --> 00:31:58.778
"Everybody Loves Raymond"
or something when I go home.

00:31:58.778 --> 00:31:59.565
I do.

00:31:59.565 --> 00:32:00.070
You do.

00:32:00.070 --> 00:32:01.640
You have to shake it off.

00:32:05.160 --> 00:32:08.740
ALICIA HALL MORAN: And also,
